<P><HI>v.</HI> 13. Cam<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="KEYERS" EXTENT="1 letter"> unto me, and &s;tood, and &s;a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="KEYERS" EXTENT="1 letter">d unto me, Brother Saul, receive thy &s;ight. And the &s;ame hour I looked up upon him.</P>
