<P><GAP LANG="grc" DESC="foreign" RESP="OXF">] &s;cil. Evangelio, quia ex &s;umm&acirc; Dei benignitate is nuncius proce&s;&s;it.</P></NOTE>
<NOTE PLACE="foot"><HI>v.</HI> 9. <GAP LANG="grc" DESC="foreign" RESP="OXF">] nempe &agrave; malo &s;uo. vide Math. 9.28.</NOTE>
